<p>Public transportation: Trains, boats, planes, shuttles</p>
<p>Public transportation will be fast and consistent. It will be possible to continue your experience while you travel - there will be NPC's and opportunities on board a train, for example. You can set up meetings with other players on the train, or set up an impromtu office space for your services.</p>
<p>Player transportation: Land/water vehicles, shuttles/ships</p>
<p>The vehicles available to players will be customizable (at least in color and components), "require" registration and maintenance.</p>